premise_source_doc_sentence: Peyton Williams Manning  (  born March 24 , 1976  )  is a former American football quarterback who played 18 seasons in the National Football League  (  NFL  )  , primarily with the Indianapolis Colts .

The Tom Brady -- Peyton Manning rivalry is a series of games that took place between 2001 and 2015 , involving two quarterbacks in the National Football League  (  NFL  )  : Tom Brady and Peyton Manning .
